---
/**
 * FAQSection Component
 * 
 * Displays frequently asked questions about the AppMRR leaderboard.
 * Includes information about:
 * - API key security
 * - Data update frequency
 * - Revenue calculation limitations
 * - How to delete an app
 * 
 * Uses HTML details/summary for collapsible Q&A items
 * 
 * Used in: index.astro
 */
---

<section class="faq-section">
        <div class="card faq-card">
                <div class="faq-header">
                        <div>
                                <h2>FAQ</h2>
                                <p class="faq-subtitle">Everything you need to know about security, data freshness, and control.</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="faq-tag">Updated March 2024</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-list">
                        <details>
                                <summary>Are my keys safe?</summary>
                                <p>
                                        We only require a RevenueCat API key with <strong>read-only</strong> access to "Chart metrics". Keys are stored encrypted at rest and never shared publicly. You can revoke the key from RevenueCat at any time.
                                </p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                                <summary>How frequently is data refreshed?</summary>
                                <p>
                                        Metrics are pulled automatically every 24 hours at midnight UTC. No manual action is required—your leaderboard position updates as soon as new data becomes available.
                                </p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                                <summary>Why can't I see all-time revenue?</summary>
                                <p>
                                        RevenueCat currently exposes revenue totals for the last 28 days via their API. We're exploring complementary sources so we can surface all-time revenue and richer insights soon.
                                </p>
                        </details>

                        <details>
                                <summary>How do I remove my app?</summary>
                                <p>
                                        You have full control—simply revoke the RevenueCat API key. The app disappears from the leaderboard during the next nightly sync (within 24 hours).
                                </p>
                        </details>
                </div>
        </div>
</section>

<style>
        .faq-section {
                margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .card {
                background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--card-bg) 92%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35));
                border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--card-border) 70%, transparent);
                border-radius: 24px;
                overflow: hidden;
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
                box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
                backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .faq-card {
                padding: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem);
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1.75rem;
        }

        .faq-header {
                display: flex;
                justify-content: space-between;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .faq-header h2 {
                margin: 0 0 0.4rem 0;
                font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.5vw, 1.6rem);
                color: var(--fg);
                letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        }

        .faq-subtitle {
                margin: 0;
                color: var(--muted);
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .faq-tag {
                align-self: flex-start;
                font-size: 0.75rem;
                letter-spacing: 0.1em;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
                border-radius: 999px;
                background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--secondary) 70%, transparent);
                color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 55%, var(--muted));
        }

        .faq-list {
                display: grid;
                gap: 1rem;
        }

        .faq-list details {
                border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--border) 65%, transparent);
                border-radius: 16px;
                padding: 1.15rem 1.35rem;
                background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--card-bg) 96%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35));
                transition: border-color 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .faq-list details[open] {
                border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 30%, var(--border));
                box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
        }

        .faq-list summary {
                cursor: pointer;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: var(--fg);
                list-style: none;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: space-between;
                gap: 1rem;
                font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .faq-list summary::-webkit-details-marker {
                display: none;
        }

        .faq-list summary::after {
                content: '+';
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                line-height: 1;
                color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 45%, var(--muted));
                transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .faq-list details[open] summary::after {
                transform: rotate(45deg);
        }

        .faq-list p {
                margin: 0.9rem 0 0 0;
                color: var(--muted);
                line-height: 1.7;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
                .faq-header {
                        flex-direction: column;
                        align-items: flex-start;
                }

                .faq-tag {
                        margin-top: 0.5rem;
                }
        }
</style>

